               <p>NEW COURT. WEDNESDAY, DECEMBER 15.</p>
               <p>Third Middlesex Jury - before Mr. Common Sergeant.</p>
               <p>243. 
               
                  <persName id="t18301209-242-defend2031" type="defendantName">
                     JAMES 
                     BOWDEN
